'''Joaquin Ronny Seys''' (born 28 March 2005) is a Belgian professional footballer who plays as a [[left-back]] for [[Belgian Pro League]] club [[Club Brugge KV|Club Brugge]] and the [[Belgium national football team|Belgium national team]].

==Club career==
Seys began playing football with [[KV Oostende|Oostende]], before joining the academy of [[Club Brugge KV|Club Brugge]] in 2012.<ref>{{Cite web |last=Taecke |first=Tomas |date=2024-07-12 |title=Sterk aan de bal en goede offensieve impulsen: wie is Joaquin Seys, het jeugdproduct van Club dat plots voor zijn vuurdoop staat? |url=https://www.hln.be/club-brugge/sterk-aan-de-bal-en-goede-offensieve-impulsen-wie-is-joaquin-seys-het-jeugdproduct-van-club-dat-plots-voor-zijn-vuurdoop-staat~a2f26c86/ |access-date=2024-09-21 |website=[[Het Laatste Nieuws]] |language=nl}}</ref> On 31 March 2022, Seys signed his first professional contract with Club Brugge until 2024, and was promoted to their reserves [[Club NXT]] where he became a starter.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.voetbalprimeur.be/nieuws/1024223/officieel-club-brugge-geeft-17-jarige-verdediger-profcontract-tot-2024.html|title=OFFICIEEL: Club Brugge geeft 17-jarige verdediger profcontract tot 2024|website=VoetbalPrimeur.be|date=31 March 2022 |language=nl}}</ref> On 10 May 2023, he extended his contract with the club until 2026.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.voetbalprimeur.be/nieuws/1078377/officieel-jonge-verdediger-tekent-bij-tot-2026-bij-club-nxt.html|title=OFFICIEEL: Jonge verdediger tekent bij tot 2026 bij Club NXT|website=VoetbalPrimeur.be|date=10 May 2023 |language=nl}}</ref>

With his Club NXT coach [[Nicky Hayen]] promoted to senior first-team head coach, Seys made his senior debut with Club Brugge at the [[2024 Belgian Super Cup]] on 20 July 2024, starting in a 2–1 loss to [[Royale Union Saint-Gilloise|Union Saint-Gilloise]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.rtl.be/sport/football/lunion-signe-une-premiere-depuis-2004-en-battant-le-club-bruges/2024-07-20/article/692766|title=L'Union signe une première depuis 2004 en battant le Club Bruges|date=July 20, 2024|website=RTL Info|language=fr}}</ref>

Seys scored on his league debut a week later against [[KV Mechelen]] in a 1–1 draw, again as a starter.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://sporza.be/nl/matches/voetbal/jupiler-pro-league/2024-2025/regulier/01/club-brugge-kv-mechelen-kv-mechelen-graait-punt-weg-bij-club-brugge-nilsson-mist-reuzekans-in-slotfase~1720024628528/|title=KV Mechelen graait punt weg bij Club Brugge, Nilsson mist reuzekans in slotfase|trans-title=KV Mechelen takes point away from Club Brugge, Nilsson misses huge chance in final phase|work=Sporza|date=26 July 2024|access-date=13 November 2024|language=Dutch}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.proleague.be/wedstrijden/seizoen-2024-2025-jupiler-pro-league-1-club-brugge-vs-kv-mechelen|title=Club Brugge v KV Mechelen - Jupiler Pro League S1|work=ProLeague.be|publisher=Belgian Pro League|access-date=13 November 2024|language=Dutch}}</ref> His selections continued into Club Brugge's [[UEFA Champions League]] campaign, making his debut in the competition against [[Borussia Dortmund]], going off with the score 0-0 with 15 minutes to go. Without Seys, Club fell to a 3–0 home loss.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://sporza.be/nl/matches/voetbal/eur/uefa-champions-league/2024-2025/league-fase/01/club-brugge-borussia-dortmund-ondanks-de-harde-0-3-zat-er-meer-in-club-brugge-vergeet-gouden-kansen-te-grijpen-en-kraakt-in-slot-tegen-dortmund~1725022872683/|title=Ondanks de harde 0-3 zat er meer in: Club Brugge vergeet gouden kansen te grijpen en kraakt in slot tegen Dortmund|trans-title=Despite the hard 0-3, there was more in it: Club Brugge forgets to seize golden opportunities and cracks in the end against Dortmund|work=Sporza|date=18 September 2024|access-date=13 November 2024|language=Dutch}}</ref>
