==International career==
Seys is a youth international for Belgium, having played up to the [[Belgium national under-18 football team|Belgium U18]]s.<ref name="auto"/>

Following a series of notable displays, including a 1–0 Champions League win over [[Aston Villa]], Seys was called up to the [[Belgium national football team|Belgium senior squad]] by coach [[Domenico Tedesco]] for [[UEFA Nations League]] ties in November 2024 against [[Italy national football team|Italy]] and [[Israel national football team|Israel]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://sporza.be/nl/2024/11/08/club-revelatie-joaquin-seys-voor-het-eerst-rode-duivel-ook-recordschutter-romelu-lukaku-opnieuw-in-selectie~1731050177118/|title=Club-revelatie Joaquin Seys voor het eerst Rode Duivel, ook recordschutter Romelu Lukaku opnieuw in selectie|trans-title=Club revelation Joaquin Seys becomes Red Devil for the first time, record scorer Romelu Lukaku also back in selection|work=Sporza|date=8 November 2024|access-date=13 November 2024|language=Dutch}}</ref>  In his next match after the announcement, Seys scored against Beerschot in a 2–2 draw only to go off with a leg injury that forced him to withdraw from the squad.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://sporza.be/nl/matches/voetbal/jupiler-pro-league/2024-2025/regulier/14/beerschot-club-brugge-club-dondert-van-champions-league-wolk-al-sahafi-bezorgt-beerschot-onverhoopt-punt-na-pijnlijke-ommekeer~1718274909462//|title=Club dondert van Champions League-wolk: Al Sahafi bezorgt Beerschot onverhoopt punt na pijnlijke ommekeer|trans-title=Club falls from Champions League cloud: Al Sahafi unexpectedly gives Beerschot point after painful turnaround|work=Sporza|date=10 November 2024|access-date=13 November 2024|language=Dutch}}</ref> 
<ref>{{cite news|url=https://sporza.be/nl/2024/11/10/alweer-een-geblesseerde-duivel-seys-onzeker-na-stevige-botsing-hebben-hem-net-naar-binnen-gedragen~1731271457726/|title=Alweer een geblesseerde Duivel? Seys onzeker na stevige botsing: "Hebben hem net naar binnen gedragen"|trans-title=Another injured Devil? Seys uncertain after heavy collision: "We just carried him inside"|work=Sporza|date=10 November 2024|access-date=13 November 2024|language=Dutch}}</ref> 
<ref>{{cite news|url=https://sporza.be/nl/2024/11/11/tegenvaller-voor-joaquin-seys-club-verdediger-moet-streep-trekk~1731314318944/|title=Tegenvaller voor Joaquin Seys: Club-verdediger moet streep trekken door eerste stap bij Rode Duivels|trans-title=Setback for Joaquin Seys: Club defender must draw a line through first step at Red Devils|work=Sporza|date=11 November 2024|access-date=13 November 2024|language=Dutch}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://sporza.be/nl/2024/11/11/de-ketelaere-doku-fofana-en-seys-haken-af-bij-de-rode-duivels-sardella-debuteert~1731352697363/|title=De Ketelaere, Doku, Fofana en Seys haken af bij de Rode Duivels, Sardella debuteert|trans-title=De Ketelaere, Doku, Fofana and Seys drop out of the Red Devils, Sardella makes his debut|work=Sporza|date=11 November 2024|access-date=13 November 2024|language=Dutch}}</ref>

